<p>Letâ€™s see how to cook your chosen dish.</p>

<h2 id="ingredients">Ingredients</h2>

<p>Here is what you need to have at home.</p>

<ol>
  <li>1kg, potato, sliced;</li>
  <li>6, eggs, sliced;;</li>
  <li>1 rod, sausage;</li>
  <li>300ml, sour cream;</li>
  <li>some, breadcrumbs;</li>
  <li>2 tbsps, lard (alternatively olive oil);</li>
  <li>Seasoning: salt, black pepper.</li>
</ol>

<h2 id="preparation">Preparation</h2>

<p>Time: Takes as long as it takes.<br />
Serves: Make sure to share, and buy for your pals.</p>

<p>Here are the steps to cook the meal. Enjoy!</p>

<ol>
  <li>Start playing music in the background.</li>
  <li>Pore a glass of drink for the chef.</li>
  <li>Start with boiling the whole pilled potatoes and eggs. After these are done, wait until they cool down.</li>
  <li>SLice the sausage, potatos, and eggs.</li>
  <li>Take a baking tray and oil up the bottom of it. Spread some bread crumble over the tray.</li>
  <li>Lay down a layer of potato, then a layer of eggs.</li>
  <li>Now add a layer of sausage, and cover it with sour cream.</li>
  <li>Time for seasoning. Donâ€™t forget the salt and pepper.</li>
  <li>Now repeat the same layers once more, and cover it all up with a layer of potato.</li>
  <li>Finish it with olive oil on the potato and breadcrumbs.</li>
  <li>Bake in the oven for 20 minutes, on 180 degrees Celsius.</li>
  <li>Serve and enjoy.</li>
</ol>

